    dc:description "FIGURES 1–7. Deanophlebia kala. Male imago: Fig.1. SEM of foreleg tarsal claw, scale bar 50µm; Fig. 2. Forewing showing relative size of hindwing, scale bar 1mm; Fig. 3. Hindwing, scale bar 500 µm; Fig. 4. Dorsal view of abdomen, scale bar 1mm; Fig. 5. Genitalia, dorsal view, scale bar 200 µm; Fig. 6. Genitalia, ventral view, scale bar 200 µm. Fig. 7. SEM close up of right lobe of penes showing apical process, scale bar 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation <https://zenodo.org/record/3414814/files/figure.png> ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3414816>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8–12. Deanophlebia kala. Female imago: Fig. 8. Forewing showing relative size of hindwing, scale bar 1mm; Fig. 9. Hindwing, scale bar 500 µm; Fig. 10. Ventral view of abdomen, sternites seven to nine, scale bar 500µm; Fig. 11. SEM of egg, scale bar 50 µm; Fig. 12. SEM detail of egg chorion, scale bar 10µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation <https://zenodo.org/record/3414816/files/figure.png> ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3414818>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Deanophlebia kala. Female nymph, scale bar 1mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation <https://zenodo.org/record/3414818/files/figure.png> ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3414820>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14–22. Deanophlebia kala. Nymph: Fig. 14. Labrum and clypeus, scale bar 200µm; Fig. 15. Left mandible, scale bar 200µm; Fig. 16. Right mandible, scale bar 200µm; Fig. 17. Maxilla, scale bar 200µm; Fig. 18. Hypopharynx, scale bar 200µm; Fig. 19. Labium, scale bar 200µm; Fig. 20. Foreleg, scale bar 500µm; Fig. 21. Foreleg tarsal claw, 100µm; Fig. 22. Gills, scale bar 100µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation <https://zenodo.org/record/3414820/files/figure.png> ;
    a fabio:Figure .

